 sublinear query time and subquadratic space\noccupancy.\n  In the worst case, it is impossible to obtain comparable results for any of\nthese problems, unless widely-believed conjectures are false.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Apr 2016 22:43:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 15 Jan 2017 12:00:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-17"}
