hemical potential on\nsuperconductivity by using the Abrikosov-Gorkov diagrammatic approach, and also\nbriefly discuss the possible generalization of this approach.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Apr 2016 09:19:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 20 Jul 2016 12:32:26 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 16 Feb 2017 17:00:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-17"}
